Introduction to CMSSW: http://cms-sw.github.io

Recipe for building and running Ntuple maker for vertex finding:

cmsrel CMSSW_12_0_0_pre4
cd CMSSW_12_0_0_pre4/src/
cmsenv 
git cms-checkout-topic -u VTXNN:VertexNtuples

git cms-addpkg L1Trigger/TrackFindingTracklet
git cms-addpkg L1Trigger/TrackFindingTMTT
git cms-addpkg L1Trigger/TrackerDTC
git cms-addpkg L1Trigger/TrackerTFP
git cms-addpkg L1Trigger/TrackTrigger
git cms-addpkg DataFormats/L1TrackTrigger
git cms-addpkg SimTracker/TrackTriggerAssociation

scram b -j 8
cd L1Trigger/TrackFindingTracklet/test/
cmsRun L1TrackNewKFNtupleMaker_cfg.py

Change L15 between 'HYBRID' (old KF) and 'NewKF' (new KF)

Track Quality BDTs are included for both the old and new kf by default and the relevant BDT is loaded automatically
